---
name: Colorful Infographic
description: Style preset — Colorful Infographic
tags: [style, creative, aspect-auto]
---
Render as a bold, vibrant infographic-style diagram on a clean white background. Use a rich, vibrant color palette with distinct colors for different sections or concepts. Add colorful icons, rounded shapes, and visual hierarchy through size and color contrast. Text should be clear and legible in a friendly, rounded font. The result should feel energetic and engaging -- like a well-designed infographic you'd want to share.
